methodology: Based on Feldmann et al. (2022) and Moxy Monitor guidelines

interpretation.bp1_description: Transition from baseline/plateau to moderate desaturation
interpretation.bp2_description: Transition from moderate to steep desaturation
interpretation.comparison_to_expected: Auto-detected breakpoints may differ from expected (280-310W, 360-400W) because: (1) Expected values may be from VT/ventilatory thresholds, not SmO2; (2) Expected values may be manually annotated; (3) SmO2 breakpoints are local muscle measures
